  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Using magnetic resonance imaging (MRI), laboratory analyses and patient reported outcomes,
      the overall aim of this study is to investigate structural injuries and biochemical
      alterations in the acutely injured knee and to relate these findings to clinical outcomes at
      various time points.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
